updater.script
Class Patch

java.lang.Object
  updater.script.Patch

public class Patch
extends java.lang.Object

This script resides in the patch describing the patch, includes how the patch is packed and the operations needed to be taken to apply the patch. It be used independently and as part of the Catalog and Client script.

Author:
Chan Wai Shing
